[
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-27T21:57:35+00:00",
    "id": "8402188505033673409",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 18,
    "quote_count": 3,
    "reply_count": 3,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 5,
    "text": "Shop was quiet this morning so I got an early start on a cuff. Coffee, Creedence, and a clean piece of sheet silver. Good way to start a day."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "5386487414666314601",
    "created_at": "2025-12-27T22:40:45+00:00",
    "id": "2408073840439637139",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 14,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "8402188505033673409",
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Creedence on a workbench is the only correct answer. What stone you setting in it?"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-28T00:41:00+00:00",
    "id": "9868269459346272639",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 10,
    "quote_count": 1,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2408073840439637139",
    "retweet_count": 4,
    "text": "Kingman turquoise, nice even matrix. Going to a Santa Fe gallery if I don't keep it for myself first."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-25T15:16:23+00:00",
    "id": "8103070136237738825",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 26,
    "quote_count": 3,
    "reply_count": 5,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Cold snap out at the cabin. Copper found the one warm spot by the stove and isn't giving it up. Smart dog."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-26T15:42:06+00:00",
    "id": "2839411212312788576",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 52,
    "quote_count": 2,
    "reply_count": 7,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Drove the F-150 up past Red Rock before dawn to catch Orion clearing the ridge. Truck's older than half the deputies but she still climbs that grade fine."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8959440547865602741",
    "created_at": "2025-12-22T03:50:20+00:00",
    "id": "5817979232036791789",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 53,
    "quote_count": 2,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "2839411212312788576",
    "retweet_count": 3,
    "text": "Dad up before sunrise to look at stars from a truck older than me. This tracks completely."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-22T14:45:28+00:00",
    "id": "6259789760427549972",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 2,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 4,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "5817979232036791789",
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "The truck has seen more sunrises than you have. Show some respect. Might get bench time tonight if nothing comes up."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "5386487414666314601",
    "created_at": "2025-12-24T15:49:28+00:00",
    "id": "5886553482009735173",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 23,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "6259789760427549972",
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Famous last words. Stay warm out there, Sam."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8959440547865602741",
    "created_at": "2025-12-27T23:55:18+00:00",
    "id": "9214739420232598356",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 11,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Dad swears the 78 F-150 has more personality than any new truck. I think he just doesn't want to learn a touchscreen."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-26T07:24:34+00:00",
    "id": "5896584218611450948",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 26,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "9214739420232598356",
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "A touchscreen can't be fixed with a socket set in a gravel lot. The F-150 can. Rest my case."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-24T03:46:27+00:00",
    "id": "1196465226762827649",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 10,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 3,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Reread an old Tony Hillerman by the stove last night. Holds up. Nobody wrote this country better."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "3621541778575914103",
    "created_at": "2025-12-27T03:07:14+00:00",
    "id": "3741195296678835961",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 16,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Pulled a bass out of Navajo Lake this morning that I'm calling the big one. Sam's going to say it's the size of his hand. He's not wrong."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-25T20:22:15+00:00",
    "id": "2056055053382417420",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 13,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "3741195296678835961",
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "That fish is the size of my hand, Eddie. The big one. Sure."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-24T11:03:22+00:00",
    "id": "6117952663738646987",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 16,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 3,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Picked up new leather for a batch of bolo cords from the shop on Coal Ave. Good supplier. Cheaper than mail order and you can feel the hide first."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "3621541778575914103",
    "created_at": "2025-12-27T06:18:55+00:00",
    "id": "2311225861104178161",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 4,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "6117952663738646987",
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Tell them Eddie sent you and the price goes up, not down. Learned that the hard way."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "4624053717606211775",
    "created_at": "2025-12-19T16:16:50+00:00",
    "id": "7238480886377128064",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 18,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "The Gallup Sun ran a nice piece on local silversmiths this week. Sam Osborne's work is in it. They spelled the name right, for once."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "5386487414666314601",
    "created_at": "2025-12-24T22:31:55+00:00",
    "id": "4764652927169977344",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 22,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Somebody told me Gallup's got no culture. Come stand in the Zuni Mountains at dawn and say that again. I'll wait."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-26T05:19:51+00:00",
    "id": "1290357043295459462",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 18,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Saw the post about the new exhibit, Angela. Worth a drive from Gallup by the look of it. How long is it up through?"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-21T13:48:11+00:00",
    "id": "7401558623091047382",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 21,
    "quote_count": 1,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 3,
    "text": "Spent the morning polishing a turquoise cuff for a Santa Fe gallery. A bench full of silver dust settles a man more than the range ever did."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-20T16:22:47+00:00",
    "id": "3920477165084231906",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 37,
    "quote_count": 2,
    "reply_count": 4,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Long week. Got the truck washed, walked the dog out by the wash, and let the rest sit. Coffee's tasting better today."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-19T02:11:33+00:00",
    "id": "6648201937550418274",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 44,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 6,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Kai ran a personal best at the meet out by the Red Rock Range. I was the loud one in the stands. No regrets."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-18T09:05:58+00:00",
    "id": "5173098264417503821",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 15,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Silver supplier shorted my last order again. Three bench days lost waiting on sheet stock. Reminds me why I keep a backup in Albuquerque."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-17T23:40:14+00:00",
    "id": "4855213097460328175",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 29,
    "quote_count": 1,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Sunday call with my mother ran long. She wanted to know if I'm eating right. I'm 48 and she still checks. Some things don't change."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-16T18:27:09+00:00",
    "id": "9037461285093217640",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 33,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 3,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "A bolo tie I cut from spiny oyster sold at the Sedona gallery before noon. My father used to say the stone picks the buyer, not the other way around."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8959440547865602741",
    "created_at": "2025-12-21T20:14:50+00:00",
    "id": "2786094513270648139",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 19,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "9037461285093217640",
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Dad finally posted the cuff he's been on all week. It's actually really good. Don't tell him I said that."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "3337136124428045527",
    "created_at": "2025-12-20T01:33:27+00:00",
    "id": "6420918375064281937",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 12,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "4855213097460328175",
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Sam, you got through a whole Sunday call without talking shop. Mom noticed. We're all proud of you, brother."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "4133075710655561948",
    "created_at": "2025-12-19T17:50:42+00:00",
    "id": "5208913746028415739",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 8,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Osborne, that cuff you brought to the office is the nicest thing in this building. Now go home, it's late."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "3750151930358304228",
    "created_at": "2025-12-18T14:08:36+00:00",
    "id": "8164209573840261945",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 27,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "text": "Samuel, I am proud of the man you have become but you still have not sent me the photo of Kai at the meet. I am your mother. The deadline was yesterday."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "6861443007791236994",
    "created_at": "2025-12-17T11:19:53+00:00",
    "id": "3592048176390582147",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 14,
    "quote_count": 0,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "text": "Sam, that turquoise cuff arrived and it's stunning. The gallery wants three more before the next show. Can your bench keep up?"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "created_at": "2025-12-15T07:42:29+00:00",
    "id": "7019384562017459283",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": 31,
    "quote_count": 1,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "retweet_count": 2,
    "text": "Creedence on the shop radio, black coffee, a clean piece of sheet silver. Day off and I still ended up at the bench. No regrets."
  },
  {
    "id": "6664265710522521018",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Ram's head cuff off the bench today. Kingman turquoise, hand-stamped edges. Photos going up on Instagram this week.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-04T18:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 48,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "retweet_count": 4,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "5439763021713699213",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Fair table at the Gallup Flea Market this Saturday. Bring cash. Bring coffee if you have it.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-06T20:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 72,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "retweet_count": 4,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "6156080712722693492",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Angela at Turquoise Trail wants two bolo ties and a buckle by 4 December. Sketchbook out.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-07T19:12:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 91,
    "reply_count": 5,
    "retweet_count": 11,
    "quote_count": 2
  },
  {
    "id": "4627738657188191424",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Kai's 5K PR knocked five seconds off yesterday's meet. Proud is not the word.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-10T20:15:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 64,
    "reply_count": 4,
    "retweet_count": 8,
    "quote_count": 2
  },
  {
    "id": "6367386600417981931",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Sixteen. Golden Dragon last night, sweet and sour chicken. She still eats the pineapples first.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-13T07:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 75,
    "reply_count": 5,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "2252960654687881341",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Zuni Mountains. Copper found a rabbit hole. Copper did not find the rabbit.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-17T16:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 73,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "retweet_count": 11,
    "quote_count": 2
  },
  {
    "id": "4154607675894948798",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Continental Divide Trail section 22 tomorrow. Cool nights up there now. Bring the wool.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-22T21:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 23,
    "reply_count": 3,
    "retweet_count": 3,
    "quote_count": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "9060193567109125271",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Case briefing ran long today. Long days end at the bench sometimes. Two hours polishing a bezel does more for me than any therapist could.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-26T19:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 53,
    "reply_count": 2,
    "retweet_count": 9,
    "quote_count": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "6573780880666137191",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Passed out full-size candy bars again. Kai says I overpay. Kai is welcome to buy the next batch.",
    "created_at": "2026-10-31T17:45:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 14,
    "reply_count": 1,
    "retweet_count": 6,
    "quote_count": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "9085983338055965061",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Forty-eight today. Coffee tastes the same. Sarah would have made fun of me for even mentioning it.",
    "created_at": "2026-11-04T08:10:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 26,
    "reply_count": 5,
    "retweet_count": 6,
    "quote_count": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "9606906056488240959",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "F-150 electrical harness laid out on the garage floor tonight. Painless kit. Colour codes and diagrams and one very patient beer.",
    "created_at": "2026-11-08T20:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 26,
    "reply_count": 5,
    "retweet_count": 0,
    "quote_count": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "3075433440152848138",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "College applications submitted. NAU, Adams State, Fort Lewis. Whatever she wants next is hers to choose.",
    "created_at": "2026-11-13T20:45:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 30,
    "reply_count": 3,
    "retweet_count": 4,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "3903405227942903680",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "New batch of belt buckles staged for solder. Kingman, Royston, Cerrillos hosts. Photos when the polish comes off.",
    "created_at": "2026-11-21T19:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 45,
    "reply_count": 6,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "5253814306620130034",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Green chile stew and my mother's frybread. That is Thanksgiving in Window Rock.",
    "created_at": "2026-11-26T19:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 9,
    "reply_count": 6,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "3106651552514216387",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Four pieces boxed and ready. Turquoise Trail window drop Friday. Angela's got a good eye for what sits in that front case.",
    "created_at": "2026-12-01T20:15:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 31,
    "reply_count": 5,
    "retweet_count": 11,
    "quote_count": 2
  },
  {
    "id": "1300655254962740931",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Delivered. Gallery window looks sharp. Thanks to everyone who follows along on the shop side of things.",
    "created_at": "2026-12-04T15:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 63,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "retweet_count": 1,
    "quote_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "9229485951365523671",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Etsy holiday orders shipped. FedEx counter guy knows me by first name now.",
    "created_at": "2026-12-15T18:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 31,
    "reply_count": 4,
    "retweet_count": 5,
    "quote_count": 2
  },
  {
    "id": "1145927566988117822",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "Quiet morning. Coffee. Dog. Kai still asleep. Cannot ask for much more than that.",
    "created_at": "2026-12-25T10:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 41,
    "reply_count": 4,
    "retweet_count": 9,
    "quote_count": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "2545176977890582410",
    "author_id": "8846424383778387405",
    "text": "F-150 in the garage. That is the resolution. That is all of it.",
    "created_at": "2027-01-01T11:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": null,
    "like_count": 43,
